<div class='header-section col-xs-12'></div>

<div class='row'>
  <h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header'>Videos</h3>
  <div class='latest_videos videos videos_container section_block col-md-10 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1'>
    <div class="home_try section_body">
      <% @repos.each_slice(5) do |repos| %>
        <%= render partial: "repositories/list", locals: {repos: repos, repo_width: "col-md-2"}  %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='center'>
  <h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header '>Why?</h3>
</div>

<div class='row '>
  <div class='what_container section_block col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1'>
    <div class="section_body">
      <p>
        We want people to be able to easily translate any internet video and share it with their friends or family in a way where original video content owners are credited properly. Traditionally, people would <span class='hardsub_notice'>hardsub</span> their translations in a separate video and re-upload it to youtube or facebook,  taking away views from the original video, and possibly getting taken down later on due to copyright notices. 
      </p>
      <br>

      <p>We're offering a <span class='softsub_notice'>softsub</span> alternative, where your subtitles are simply overlayed over the original, official video that will never get taken down. Moreover, the views you get also goes towards the original video, thus supporting them in some way.</p>

      <br>

      <p>Basically, here are list of some of the reasons on why one might want to use this site:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You want an easy way to translate a video without having to re-encode, re-upload to a separate channel</li>
        <li>You want to support the original content owner</li>
        <li>Your "hardsubbed" subtitles are getting taken down and you want a producer-friendly alternative  </li>
        <li>You want to subtitle a video without having to wait for weeks for the owner to add it back to their video.</li>
        <!-- <li>You want fancy effects for you subtitles (crazy fonts, different positions, karaoke style effects)</li> -->
      </ul>
        
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

